/**
 * Class for a Slot.
 */
class Slot {
  /**
   * Constructor of the class.
   * @param {object} settings Settings for the instance.
   */
  constructor(settings) {
    this.settings = settings || {};
    this.intent = this.settings.intent;
    this.entity = this.settings.entity;
    this.alias = this.settings.alias || this.entity;
    this.mandatory =
      this.settings.mandatory === undefined ? false : this.settings.mandatory;
    this.isList =
      this.settings.isList === undefined ? false : this.settings.isList;
    this.questions = this.settings.questions || [];
    this.near = this.settings.near;
  }
}
 
module.exports = Slot;
